column5: if anybody has any information about point anne's ice conditions that would be very apprecitiated  thanks muddy
Check DTSam's daily ice updates at his site....  http://www.carraoutdoors.com/fishing_reports.html

Hey Muddy,  Check out carraoutdoors.com . He posts reports daily and should be able to give you a definative answer as to whether or not the ice is safe. If it doesn't mention your specific spot on the report; give him a call. Please, do not go out there without consulting the locals. The ice has been very tempremental lately. Good luck!!!
